sections.heading: companies; lines of insurance; authorized
sections.text: Except as provided in section 44-1984, a company may be formed or an existing company may be authorized to transact any one or more of the lines of insurance specified in section 44-201.SourceLaws 1913, c. 154, ยง 80, p. 428;R.S.1913, ยง 3217;Laws 1919, c. 190
